dspace-development.title: Symplectic Elements: Missing Results for Specific Query

comments.body: As I cannot seem to advance this much further without incurring additional possible delays, I have created a support request with Symplectic: https://support.symplectic.co.uk/support/tickets/366105

My diagnosis is that, assessing the logs for the search index rebuild jobs, that this *should* be rebuilding on a weekly basis, but that this is somehow failing to rebuild. As a result, the last successful rebuild seems to have taken place during November 2021.

Unfortunately, I cannot locate in the service log entries where this failure might originate. Please be aware that I have also investigated the IIS service logs within the Windows Server environment.
